IN RE Application of MCDANIEL 2019-0247 Supreme Court of Ohio. May 28, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

DISCIPLINARY CASES

On application of Hugh David McDaniel III to take the Ohio bar examination. Application approved. Applicant may apply to take the next bar examination. Applicant's motion to seal the record granted.

Kennedy, J., concurs in part and dissents in part and would deny applicant's motion to seal the record.
